# Application layer (BLoC)

- Location: `lib/features/<feature>/application/`
- Files: `<name>_bloc.dart`, `<name>_event.dart`, `<name>_state.dart` (Freezed).
- BLoC depends on `I*Repository` from domain ‚Äî never on infrastructure implementations directly.
- No Flutter widgets or `BuildContext` in application layer.
- Use explicit types in `BlocBuilder` and state `switch` expressions.
